definition: Yangzhou prefecture level city in Jiangsu
abbr. for 揚州|扬州[Yang2 zhou1]/surname Yang
to raise/to hoist/the action of tossing or winnowing/scattering (in the wind)/to flutter/to propagate
variant of 揚|扬[yang2]
prefecture/(old) province/(old) administrative division/state (e.g. of US)/oblast (Russia)/canton (Switzerland)
Yangzhou prefecture level city in Jiangsu
lit. to ride a crane to Yangzhou (idiom); to get an official position
lit. to ride a crane to Yangzhou/to become a Daoist immortal/to die

sentences.english: Yang state board of trade each big trading company surrender a book.
sentences.chinese: 扬州商会各大商行的投诚书。

sentences.english: Yangzhou was a port of friendly foreign exchanges.
sentences.chinese: 扬州也是中外友好往来的港口。

sentences.english: No matter where I go, Yangzhou's snacks will never leave my mind.
sentences.chinese: 无论我走到哪里，我都会想起扬州的美食。

sentences.english: At Yangzhou University, I often got invited for a weekend at a student's home.
sentences.chinese: 在扬州大学，周末时学生常常请我去他们家。

sentences.english: Established in 1994, Yangzhou Mingxin Plastic Chemical Co.
sentences.chinese: 扬州明鑫塑化有限公司，创建于1994年。

sentences.english: Kim is rumored to have visited solar power and electronics companies in Jiangsu province, where Yangzhou is located.
sentences.chinese: 传闻金正日考察了江苏扬州的太阳能和电子制造公司。

sentences.english: We have Yangzhou fried rice in Chinese restaurants back in the U. K.
sentences.chinese: 在英国的中餐馆里，我们就有扬州炒饭。

sentences.english: The objective of this experiment is to guarantee the quality of Yangzhou Briny Goose.
sentences.chinese: 为了保证扬州盐水鹅的卫生质量和品质。

sentences.english: Yangzhou Eight Eccentric Artists develop an important group in Chinese painting history in 18th centuries.
sentences.chinese: 扬州八怪，是18世纪中国绘画史上的一支劲旅。

sentences.english: Yangzhou double east block was modified according to repair old as the old principles.
sentences.chinese: 扬州的双东街区按照修旧如旧的原则进行了改造。

sentences.english: This great poet used to be the magistrate of Yangzhou.
sentences.chinese: 这位伟大的诗人曾经做过扬州知州。

sentences.english: Therefore, people of Yangzhou started calling it five dice buns.
sentences.chinese: 所以扬州人就管这种包子叫五丁包子了。

sentences.english: But if we go to Yangzhou, we can get big discounts on the hotels.
sentences.chinese: 但如果我们去扬州的话，我们可以得到较大的折扣的。

sentences.english: This article describes water-carriage system experiment of water quality purification in Yangzhou Slender West Lake.
sentences.chinese: 介绍了扬州瘦西湖水质治理中的引水系统试验。

sentences.english: Slender West Lake is the premier attraction in Yangzhou.
sentences.chinese: 瘦西湖是扬州最引人入胜之处。
